  <h2>Method Overview</h2>
  <div class="highlight">
    <p>The Five Human Factors method analyzes users through five lenses: Physical, Cognitive, Social, Cultural, and Emotional. This approach reveals deeper motivations, constraints, and behaviors beyond demographics, helping designers understand real human needs.</p>
